Package: REchoNest
Type: Package
Title: Tools to access artist and song data using Echo Nest API
Version: 0.1.2
Date: 2015-12-13
Authors@R: person("Mukul", "Chaware", email = "mukul.chaware13@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: To have access to Echo Nest API. Artist's data including songs, blogs ,news ,reviews, hotttnesss etc can be accessed. Song's data including audio summary,style,danceability,tempo etc can also be similarly accessed. It can be also used to recommend similar artists. Music data can also be accessed specific to particular partner catalog. 
